As a Freshman (2017)

Did not see game action.

Before St. John’s

A four-year letterwinner at DePaul Catholic… played for Everton FC Westchester on the club circuit… a two-year team captain for Everton FC Westchester.

Personal

Daniel Domicolo… born in Staten Island, N.Y… son of Tony and Francine Domicolo… has two older sisters, Margherite and Alexandra … chose St. John’s for its athletic program, academic reputation and Christian values… lists his father as the person who most influenced his athletic career and Cristiano Ronaldo as his favorite athlete… his godfather, Mike Sorber, is a former member of the United States Men’s National Team and is currently an assistant coach with the Philadelphia Union… active in community service… aspires to play in the MLS after college.
